sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box rgb(149, 165, 166) ERP side
        participant ERP as Plentymarkets ERP
        participant Talend as Talend ETL
    end
    box rgb(41, 128, 185) Spryker Backend
        participant Glue as Glue Backend API
        participant Import as Data Import
        participant DB as MariaDB
    end
    box rgb(155, 89, 182) Publish & Sync
        participant RMQ as RabbitMQ
        participant PS as P&S Publishers/Sync
        participant Redis as Redis (KV)
        participant ES as Elasticsearch
    end

    Note over Talend: Scheduler triggers delta every 10 min (~50 products)
    ERP->>Talend: Changed products, prices, stock, categories
    Talend->>Glue: POST delta payload (REST, token+scope)
    Glue->>Import: Hand off delta records
    Import->>DB: Batch upsert (PDO, pre-gathered lookups)
    DB->>RMQ: Emit entity change events [AMQP]
    RMQ->>PS: Publish (multiple queues, chunked)
    PS->>DB: Stage to *_storage / *_search
    PS->>Redis: Sync key-value storefront data
    PS->>ES: Index category/catalog docs
    Note over Redis,ES: Storefront serves updated catalog within the 10-min window
